                  <summary>I) ʾOrit za-lǝdät “Genesis” (fols. 1ra-46vb), incomplete&#xD;
II) ʾOrit za-ḍäʾat “Exodus“ (fols. 47ra-84vb)&#xD;
III) ʾOrit za-ḫʷǝlqʷ “Numbers“ (fols. 85ra-126vb)&#xD;
IV) ʾOrit za-lewāwǝyān “Leviticus” (fols. 127ra-158vb)&#xD;
V) ʾOrit za-dagǝm “Deuteronomy” (fols. 159ra-195vb)&#xD;
VI) ʾOrit za-ʾIyasu “Joshua” (fols. 196ra-218vb)&#xD;
VII) ʾOrit za-masāfǝnt “Judges” (fols. 218vb-240va)&#xD;
VIII) ʾOrit za-Rut “Ruth” (fols. 240vb-243rb)&#xD;
&#xD;
